Package javazoom.jl.decoder

Class BitstreamException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • javazoom.jl.decoder.JavaLayerException
          • javazoom.jl.decoder.BitstreamException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, BitstreamErrors, JavaLayerErrors
    public class BitstreamException
extends JavaLayerException
implements BitstreamErrors
    Instances of BitstreamException are thrown when operations on a Bitstream fail. The exception provides details of the exception condition in two ways: as an error-code describing the nature of the error as the Throwable instance, if any, that was thrown indicating that an exceptional condition has occurred.
    Since:
    0.0.6
